/pages/why-fiordland-expeditions.html  /pages/about-us.html              301
/pages/why-us.html                     /pages/about-us.html              301

# ============================================================================
# Squarespace migration — clean-URL mappings from the old site. Preserves
# SEO equity (impressions, backlinks) by 301-ing every known old URL to its
# current FEL page. No catch-all: unmapped URLs serve 404.html cleanly,
# which Google handles correctly. A catch-all-to-homepage would trigger
# soft-404 penalties.
#
# Left-hand paths preserved character-for-character from Squarespace —
# including singular/plural inconsistency (/historic-fiordland-charter
# vs /research-charters) and American "inquiries" spelling
# (/charter-inquiries). Those are historical URLs Google has indexed;
# we don't get to edit history.
# ============================================================================

